title: Future's Past The Beginning
description: As I am writing this, my fear is into determination. I've been saying for a while now that there are changes coming in in the winds. These changes will not be good. Our community is calling us to do more than out part. Our healers will be paramount as well as our warriors and protectors. The changes have just started happening. There are many more yet to come.
author: Christine F. Stacey
